# Recipe data is served from the PRIVATE Supabase Storage bucket `recipe-data`
# (authenticated users only), NOT as public static files. These stay in git as
# the source of truth, but must never be deployed to the CDN — otherwise anyone
# could download the full dataset without signing in.
data.json
icons.json
furniture.json

# Build-time tooling / inputs — not part of the served site.
*.py
